 id=\"note4d\" data-full-marker=\"4г\">\n<p data-aid=\"123529052\" id=\"note4d_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/eternal-life?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Жизнь вечная</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"7\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note7a\" data-full-marker=\"7а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123529054\" id=\"note7a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.50-70?lang=rus#p50\">У. и З. 76:50–70</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"б\" id=\"note7b\" data-full-marker=\"7б\">\n<p data-aid=\"123529056\" id=\"note7b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.26?lang=rus#p26\">2 Неф. 2:26</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.27?lang=rus#p27\">Алма 42:27</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/14.30?lang=rus#p30\">Гел. 14:30</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/agency?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Свобода воли</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"8\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note8a\" data-full-marker=\"8а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123529057\" id=\"note8a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.38?lang=rus#p38\">У. и З. 1:38</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"9\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note9a\" data-full-marker=\"9а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123529058\" id=\"note9a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.23-28?lang=rus#p23\">У. и З. 42:23–28</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"10\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note10a\" data-full-marker=\"10а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123529059\" id=\"note10a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ps/31.10?lang=rus#p10\">Пс. 31:10</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptur